朱迪·丹奇的视力丧失意味着她无法再独自外出https://www.nme.com/news/film/judi-dench-vision-loss-means-she-cant-go-outside-on-her-own-anymore-3831075?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=judi-丹奇视力丧失意味着她不能再独自外出Victoria LuxfordWed, 22 Jan 2025 14:49:25 +0000 Film NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3831075 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱迪·丹奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “总会有人陪着我”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/judi-dench-vision-loss-means-she-cant-go-outside-on-her-own-anymore-3831075">《朱迪·丹奇失明意味着她无法再独自外出》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朱迪·丹奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Judi-Dench-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演艺传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judi-dench">朱迪·丹奇夫人</a>最近透露，由于视力恶化，她无法再独自外出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/james-bond-theme-songs-ranked-3062084">每首詹姆斯·邦德主题曲都按照……伟大程度排列？</a></li></ul><p>这位 90 岁的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡奖</a>得主在特林尼·伍德尔 (Trinny Woodall) 的<em>无畏</em>播客中谈到了黄斑变性的情况，这种情况导致她的视力近年来不断恶化。她在 2012 年首次讨论了这种情况，称自己正在“与失明作斗争”，并补充道：“由于我的眼睛有问题，我无法再阅读剧本了。于是有人进来给我读它们，就像给我讲故事一样。”</p><p>在出现在播客中时，她说：“有人会永远和我在一起。我现在必须这么做，因为我看不见，我会撞到什么东西或者摔倒”。她还谈到了这种情况的焦虑，承认：“在去做某事之前我总是很紧张。我不知道为什么……我根本不擅长独自一人，现在也不会。”她随后开玩笑说：“幸好我现在不用了，因为我假装没有视力”。</p><p>她谈到了她过去的失明给她的职业生涯带来的困难，她<a href="https://people.com/movies/judi-dench-reveals-how-she-continues-to-act-despite-her-eyesight-loss/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在视觉基金会的一次演讲中</a>透露：“你找到了一种方法来解决和克服你觉得非常困难的事情……我已经我必须找到另一种学习台词和事物的方法，那就是让我的好朋友一遍又一遍地向我重复它们。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="朱迪·丹奇夫人谈初恋、找到家庭和幸运的突破无畏播客 |特里尼" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q2rlUCTrkMk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>丹奇有着历史性的演艺生涯，曾出演过<em>《莎翁情史》</em> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/belfast-review-jamie-dornan-3142623"><em>《贝尔法斯特》</em></a>等电影，并于 1995 年至 2015 年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/james-bond">詹姆斯·邦德</a>系列电影中扮演 M。她是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/maggie-smith-dies-aged-89-3797758">已故女爵士玛吉·史密斯</a>的终身朋友，最近当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/judi-dench-in-tears-while-speaking-about-maggie-smiths-death-3800077">她谈到这位明星去年的去世时，她情绪激动。</a>她还透露，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/judi-dench-memorial-trees-dedicated-alan-rickman-helen-mccrory-3337483">为已故的朋友树立了“纪念树”</a> ，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alan-rickman">艾伦·里克曼</a>和海伦·麦克罗里。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/judi-dench-vision-loss-means-she-cant-go-outside-on-her-own-anymore-3831075">《朱迪·丹奇失明意味着她无法再独自外出》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
